{"tid":162343,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/Switch]二手遊戲買賣網 Heyy.uk","createTime":"2017-03-19T08:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T14:42:31.000Z","uid":55659,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f075adc4911548d2d308ae8aabe034d72f185f5b","tid":162343,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/En33DSA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEn33DSA.jpg&h=8f372a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"http://heyy.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fheyy.uk&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9e665a03\" target=\"_blank\">http://heyy.uk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">自從3月10開Post到3月19, <br />\n合共有4百個刊登, 當中有70%係成功賣出<br />\n平均一日有700個活躍User</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><a href=\"http://Heyy.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHeyy.uk&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=05362d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Heyy.uk</a> 既好處係</span><br />\n賣家可以直接用手機Post Game <br />\n同時可以設定價錢/議價/同想交換既Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/750j841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F750j841.jpg&h=663ffcd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身冇用TG既Brah<br />\n如果你註冊既Email 係堅既話<br />\n一有人買你隻Game, <a href=\"http://Heyy.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHeyy.uk&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=05362d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Heyy.uk</a> 就會自動俾Email你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6h5FJR2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6h5FJR2.jpg&h=f2f98ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">對買家黎講</span><br />\n一眼就可以睇哂<br />\n咁多個價錢/買家地點/想交換既Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7brEk7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7brEk7x.jpg&h=868647c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未知隻Game玩咩 ? 按&quot;遊戲影片&quot;就一目了然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4CRcxLM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4CRcxLM.png&h=ecc85ce5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊大約有以下既Update,<br />\n- Paypal 買賣 <br />\n- 收Game <br />\n<br />\n呢個只係Side Project <br />\n本身有正職,所以會Update 得比較慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nThat's it, Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a756a93852c37d460599f4792ef47e3897dbbda","tid":162343,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"舊Post 好亂<br />\n所以先出個新Post <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 建議Brother 用真Email 註冊<br />\n咁先可以Send 到Notification 去你Email<br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(不定時人手推Post)"},{"pid":"12c8aa4d6acc4e2b6138a85710907a1d2cd1b80f","tid":162343,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa70931188850e99a2a1091decf1e85144b5db3b","tid":162343,"uid":55659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ace35cf8350246c40ce346f866a60ea791e5b7","tid":162343,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128c2a3